      "author": "L7Cy",
      "description": "### Show Remaining Time\r\nDisplays the remaining time (or overtime) instead.\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/L7Cy/obsidian-dynamic-timetable/assets/84382631/dd7f1e7d-6076-44a6-8b04-3a0f2654950b)\r\n\r\n### Path to Dictionary for Suggestions\r\nCreate a dictionary for [Various Complements](https://github.com/tadashi-aikawa/obsidian-various-complements-plugin) to suggest task names and estimated times.\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/L7Cy/obsidian-dynamic-timetable/assets/84382631/0674e64e-2bbc-473d-8bcf-4444093bf1a4)\r\n\r\n### Custom URL Scheme\r\nOpens a custom URL scheme when the \"Complete Task\" command is executed. The video demonstrates setting up a [Due](https://www.dueapp.com/)'s URL scheme.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/L7Cy/obsidian-dynamic-timetable/assets/84382631/386aedca-1313-44da-8ed7-e73e0a23740f\r\n\r\n",
